{"tid":203311,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 黑椒乾炒牛河","createTime":"2017-04-16T07:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T20:44:20.000Z","uid":74981,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57aea999e58c44600d0064598d034e79ab2f89d4","tid":203311,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/9f67d1db7554b75b8afb3cf275f87a98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F9f67d1db7554b75b8afb3cf275f87a98.jpg&h=58ed8fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/81a9a625be1cc6936ca7af4ce5863874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F81a9a625be1cc6936ca7af4ce5863874.jpg&h=4f682705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片如下:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VORXB77bUmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVORXB77bUmE&d=1ElP8QZN%2FBtuydBCWvxAMsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f436ef83\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VORXB77bUmE</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然本癲狗已經唔止一次post牛河, 但真係諗唔到食乜所以post番牛河算, 希望各位多多包涵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做法如下:<br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n河粉半斤<br />\n牛柳邊帶肥帶筋位幾兩<br />\n銀芽少許<br />\n九王少許<br />\n<br />\n醃料:<br />\n2茶匙生抽<br />\n1茶匙酒<br />\n少許白胡椒粉<br />\n少許黑胡椒粉<br />\n水2茶匙<br />\n豆粉水 (1茶匙豆粉加1茶匙水開)<br />\n油1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n調味:<br />\n1湯匙生抽<br />\n1湯匙老抽<br />\n黑胡椒碎<br />\n<br />\n1. 河粉meet散, 牛肉用醃料醃15分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2. 大火燒紅獲, 落油朗獲, 熄火爆牛肉一陣, 開番少少火炒至牛肉7成熟隔油撈起, 倒左d油, 洗獲.<br />\n<br />\n3. 大火燒紅獲, 落油朗獲, 倒哂d油, 落河粉轉中火煎至一面金黃色.<br />\n<br />\n4. 反另一面煎, 開大火, 煎到咁上下就炒散佢再煎, 然後煎到咁上下又炒散佢再煎, 重覆至每條河粉都被煎香<br />\n<br />\n5. 熄火, 落調味, 牛肉, 銀芽, 九王, 開大火炒至香兼乾身, 完成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c614189a290858c66a5fc252323e27ea528c9491","tid":203311,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f149dce90cdddafc25044a10e5c8ea44d71629a","tid":203311,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夏榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d904d418d92fb4afacf33fe83c0d7143a761948","tid":203311,"uid":12543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"又係你<br />\n<br />\n我想試食"},{"pid":"d35e69143186e59a2356a04c2c1a7c43ceafc822","tid":203311,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:12:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係你<br />\n<br />\n我想試食</blockquote><br />\n本癲狗係駐守飲食台既九流大廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7576fe34fb82997c9f6d82bf4937f74b71667719","tid":203311,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:15:22.000Z","msg":"狗 我想嘔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bef028ba21efb20a8d793ed7a6ea9b0879855bc","tid":203311,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4e9a34417da76e2965693d86d17efdf21d755d","tid":203311,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>狗 我想嘔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弘b食錯野?"},{"pid":"f783d16c98915f831b68f311fae3755ad76d17cc","tid":203311,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed68abcafeb374ec7e26d0a